# SSL Certificates Directory

Place your SSL certificates in this directory for HTTPS support.

## Required files for production:
- `cert.pem` - SSL certificate chain
- `key.pem` - Private key

## Generate self-signed certificate for testing:

```bash
openssl req -x509 -newkey rsa:4096 -keyout key.pem -out cert.pem -days 365 -nodes \
  -subj "/C=IT/ST=State/L=City/O=Org/CN=localhost"
```

## To enable HTTPS, uncomment the SSL section in docker/nginx/conf.d/default.conf
